ed, Mrs. Sinclair?"],[3212,3450,"Yes, I need you to track down my son."],[3450,3562,"Find Tyler,"],[3562,3662,"and you'll graduate"],[3662,3913,"from ex-girlfriend to fiancée."],[3975,4075,"Deal?"],[4725,4904,"You almost done, Dr. Frankenstein?"],[5004,5141,"Quit yapping"],[5141,5237,"or I'll give you another one"],[5237,5350,"to match."],[5350,5487,"No, you won't."]],"20":[[816,1012,"If I don't pay the bank"],[1012,1287,"within a month, I could lose the farm."],[1412,1662,"You're $100,000 in debt?"],[1662,1716,"What do you do to make"],[1716,1800,"money around here?"],[1800,1929,"Me and Daddy used to sell"],[1929,2204,"produce and dairy to the locals, but..."],[2204,2325,"then the land buyers started"],[2325,2466,"coming in and..."],[2529,2700,"everything got really messed up."],[2700,2754,"Why didn't you sell?"],[2754,2904,"This place is a gold mine."],[3166,3387,"Is that all that matters to you?"],[3454,3570,"No, but your family could have been"],[3570,3712,"better off if you just would've sold-"],[3712,3970,"Better off?"]],"21":[[25,325,"This farm is my legacy,"],[325,475,"my daddy's legacy."],[475,634,"And I want to raise kids here"],[634,800,"like he raised me."],[900,1012,"So, that"],[1012,1341,"means a hell of a lot more"],[1341,1537,"than some numbers"],[1537,1687,"and a dollar sign."],[1841,2012,"Avery..."],[2012,2112,"Avery,"],[2112,2250,"I'm sorry."],[2334,2387,"Yeah."],[2387,2537,"I never thought about it like that."],[2537,2629,"I didn't know how much this place"],[2629,2762,"meant to you."],[3212,3312,"I will"],[3312,3625,"consider forgiving you..."],[3625,3775,"if you help with lunch."],[3862,4016,"So,"],[4016,4141,"cook"],[4141,4254,"or starve,"],[4254,4391,"what'll it be?"],[6162,6300,"It's delicious."],[6404,6575,"Where did you learn to make this?"],[6629,6716,"My daddy."],[6716,6850,"It was kind of our thing together."],[6850,6979,"Well, he taught you well."],[7016,7162,"You're lucky, Avery."],[7254,7404,"Yeah, I was."],[7500,7566,"Hey, hush up."],[7566,7737,"Just eat, alright?"],[7987,8162,"Avery,"],[8162,8408,"this is how we can save your farm."]],"22":[[91,200,"Tyler, if this is about me"],[200,275,"cutting you a break..."],[275,375,"It's not."],[375,475,"I want to throw an event."],[475,541,"It can be a..."],[541,716,"a farm-to-table."],[716,787,"A little fundraiser."],[787,966,"It can save your farm."],[966,1064,"But how would we get"],[1064,1187,"anyone to come?"],[1187,1300,"If I can get online"],[1300,1400,"and get my assistant to have"],[1400,1641,"influencers blast their socials,"],[1641,1800,"with half a million followers,"],[1800,1962,"you'll have people lined up out the door."],[1962,2078,"You expect me to believe"],[2078,2262,"you have half a million followers?"],[2350,2487,"Tyler, what exactly"],[2487,2662,"do you do for a living?"],[2662,2725,"I..."],[2725,2825,"run a business."],[2825,2912,"Yeah, you"],[2912,3050,"park cars for rich people, right?"],[3050,3300,"I am..."],[3300,3450,"in real estate."],[3566,3691,"We're one of the biggest."],[3691,3875,"If you're one of the biggest,"],[3875,3950,"then why hasn't anyone"],[3950,4150,"from your company come knocking?"],[4650,4766,"What the hell are you doing with"],[4766,4875,"my boyfriend?"],[4875,5025,"Boyfriend?"]],"23":[[412,525,"Ex-boyfriend."],[525,729,"Jules, how the hell did you find me?"],[729,879,"Phone tracker."],[879,937,"I installed it"],[937,1075,"way before we broke up."],[1075,1187,"Can't be too careful."],[1187,1282,"Careful? Let's not forget"],[1282,1387,"who cheated on who."],[1387,1529,"You're still not over that?"],[1529,1625,"Alright, stop harassing"],[1625,1762,"my farmhand."],[1762,1850,"Yeah? And"],[1850,2037,"leave because I didn't invite you in."],[2116,2262,"Farmhand?"],[2425,2612,"Poverty looks bad on you."],[2612,2700,"Let's go, Ty."],[2700,2854,"Board wants you back at HQ."],[2904,3016,"No."],[3112,3275,"He's not going anywhere"],[3275,3512,"until he pays off his debt."],[3600,3762,"She's adorable."],[3825,3904,"When are you going to"],[3904,4212,"let her in on the big con?"],[4212,4316,"What"],[4316,4441,"big con?"]],"24":[[25,262,"I'm not conning anyone."],[304,550,"Well then why are you here?"],[550,650,"Don't tell me you don't know she's-"],[650,741,"Excuse us."],[741,837,"Please."],[1041,1187,"What the hell are you doing here?"],[1187,1350,"Are you kidding me?"],[1350,1454,"Tyler!"],[1454,1604,"You were supposed to acquire"],[1604,1725,"this farm days ago."],[1725,1892,"The board's super pissed."],[1987,2087,"What did you just say?"],[2087,2225,"You're here to get"],[2225,2462,"Bauer Spring Hill Farm."],[2462,2587,"And that girl,"],[2587,2679,"Avery,"],[2679,2950,"she's the owner you have to take it from."]],"25":[[179,425,"You have started the deal, right?"],[529,691,"Hey. You okay?"],[766,900,"I'm fine. Just-"],[900,1087,"Go wait in the car. I need to pack."],[1466,1612,"Fuck!"],[2350,2466,"No, I think that's perfect."],[2487,2675,"What the hell am I supposed to say to her?"],[2812,2941,"I'm sorry it took so long"],[2941,3166,"to get you your last paycheck."],[3166,3300,"Keep it."],[3300,3400,"Just stopped by to check"],[3400,3537,"to make sure you're eating."],[3537,3762,"Got enough for groceries this month?"],[3762,3900,"Who needs groceries"],[3900,4104,"when I'm such a good farmer?"],[4104,4279,"She can't afford to buy food?"],[4650,4875,"Tell me how to save this place, Daddy."],[4966,5112,"I need help."],[5191,5312,"Yeah?"],[5312,5450,"What's the holdup?"],[5641,5766,"Are you coming?"]],"26":[[66,212,"No, leave without me."],[925,1154,"I thought you'd be gone by now."],[1154,1312,"Tell her the truth."],[1462,1575,"They don't need me back at the office yet."],[1575,1750,"What the fuck am I doing?"],[1812,1966,"Besides, we have a"],[1966,2066,"farm-to-table event"],[2066,2187,"to host, don't we?"],[3187,3312,"Sorry, I..."],[3312,3504,"didn't take you for a hugger."],[3504,3629,"You okay?"],[3629,3754,"I'm fine."],[3804,3962,"We should take some promo pics."],[3962,4