 hair?"],[6550,6741,"As a woman who is"],[6741,6912,"more talented than she knows."],[7179,7291,"Nice."],[7500,7625,"Good."],[7791,7979,"You're goregous."],[7979,8100,"Look at these."],[8700,8850,"I'm a natural."],[8925,9087,"I don't know how I'm going to upload these."],[9087,9216,"Well, you want to use my computer?"],[9216,9337,"You have a computer?"],[9337,9400,"Yeah."],[9400,9529,"You've a computer the whole time?"],[9529,9654,"Okay!"],[9654,9741,"Come on."]],"29":[[200,325,"Ta-da!"],[325,479,"This thing belongs in a museum."],[479,700,"Well knock yourself out, city boy."],[812,916,"And,"],[916,1000,"settle in."],[1000,1162,"Because it's dial up."],[1837,1925,"Finally."],[1925,2000,"I'm in."],[2000,2141,"You've got mail."],[2179,2337,"Fine, let's see if you can"],[2337,2475,"send an email."],[2537,2754,"Setting up a farm-to-table"],[2754,3062,"event at Spring Hill Farm."],[3062,3350,"Start a viral campaign ASAP."],[3429,3550,"You've got mail."],[3787,3975,"What the hell is this?"],[3975,4200,"A no confidence vote."],[4300,4462,"Fuck! They're going to fire me."]],"30":[[104,287,"Avery, we got a problem."],[562,675,"Tyler, I fixed it."],[675,837,"You just killed the internet."],[979,1254,"Well, excuse me"],[1254,1354,"for trying to fix the phone"],[1354,1475,"without your damn permission."],[1475,1675,"I'm very close to losing my job."],[1675,1854,"This event is your only lifeline."],[1854,2012,"I cannot save us"],[2012,2225,"if I don't have the internet."],[2550,2675,"Come here, dear."],[3100,3225,"You had one job to do!"],[3225,3350,"If Tyler doesn't answer,"],[3350,3462,"you're fired."],[3600,3712,"This is Avery."],[3712,3875,"This is Marissa Sinclair,"],[3875,4025,"chairwoman of Bauer Industries."],[4025,4300,"Have you sold your farm to my son?"]],"31":[[12,66,"I'm sorry."],[66,254,"Did you say Bauer Industries?"],[254,325,"I did."],[325,400,"Have you had a chance"],[400,579,"to review our proposal?"],[579,741,"No, I haven't."],[741,850,"And actually,"],[850,1